(- verify parent launcher process did not immediately respawn roles.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When integrated with external supervisors, confirm restart policies are intentionally disabled) Tj
T*
(during maintenance windows.) Tj
T*
(- Bottom Line) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Src/Main/stop.py is the supported shutdown control point for Atho node roles. Use it instead of) Tj
T*
(ad-hoc process termination to reduce collateral risk, preserve graceful shutdown semantics, and) Tj
T*
(maintain predictable operational behavior across CLI, API, and GUI surfaces.) Tj
T*
